  <brief_title>Transrectal Ultrasound (TRUS) in Finding Tumors During Robotic-Assisted Laparoscopic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mechanically-Manipulated Transrectal Ultrasound (TRUS) During Robotic-Assisted Laparoscopic Prostatectomy (RALP)</official_title>
